This is Perl module WebService::Klout, a Easy-to-use Interface for Klout API.

INSTALLATION

WebService::Klout installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    $ cpan WebService::Klout

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

WebService::Klout documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc WebService::Klout

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

